<h2>radix: 'R Markdown' Format for Scientific and Technical Writing</h2>
<p>Scientific and technical article format for the web. 'Radix' articles 
    feature attractive, reader-friendly typography, flexible layout options
    for visualizations, and full support for footnotes and citations.</p>
<table summary="Package radix summary">
<tr>
<td>Version:</td>
<td>0.6</td>
</tr>
